headline: JPMorgan Hires CDH Investments Chief to Strengthen Asia Pacific Push
summary: JPMorgan has appointed the chief executive of Chinese alternative asset manager CDH Investments as its new vice chair of Asia Pacific, marking the latest major hire by the U.S. bank as it seeks to expand its business in the region.
